Yes, I know I’ve been offline sometime but I’m back for an amazing reason. As you know I was crowned with Miss Tuskegee at my amazing alma mater #TuskegeeUniversity and now I want to have the honor to announce my honorary baby/sweet niece is running for the title! 

When you go out and vote today #Tuskegee make sure you vote for my baby A’Yanna King as she is SO deserving! ❤️ 

#TuskegeeUniversity #Vote #MissTuskegee #AyannaKing

My heart is so full as we celebrate the beautiful life of my mother Mirian Steele McGhee. I miss you, my sweet angel face. I am humbled and so grateful for all of our family and friends who plan to attend. May you continue to rest in paradise mommy.
I’m so confused….. should I pull over?? Please advise ❤️🤦🏽‍♀️🤷🏽‍♀️ #steelestanding

Thank you @bronzelens ….. I am honored to host Bronze Carpet at the 14th Annual @BronzeLens Film Festival Awards. Congratulations to all of the nominees…. You are truly amazing! #bronzelens #steelestanding #blackExcellence❤️❤️

I'm honored to be the emcee for the Black Women's Health Imperative's
40th-anniversary celebration. This organization has been a pillar in improving health outcomes for Black women for decades. Join us in Atlanta for the #BWHI40 homecoming celebration to be a part of this remarkable legacy. More info at https://bit.ly/BWHI40th.

#BlkWomensHealth #SteeleStanding

40 years of the Black Women's Health Imperative is not just a milestone—it's 40 years of
essential health policy, education, and research for Black women. I'm beyond excited to host the #BWHI40 homecoming celebration in Atlanta, and I want YOU to be there with me. Don't miss out; RSVP now and get all the details you need at https://bit.ly/BWHI40th.

#SteeleStanding #BlkWomensHealth

The Black Women's Health Imperative has paved the way in leadership development
and knowledge sharing for Black women's health. Let's celebrate their achievements at the #BWHI40 homecoming celebration in Washington, DC. Be there! Visit https://bit.ly/BWHI40th to learn more.

#BlkWomensHealth #SteeleStanding
